{"tid":191271,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"《分·裂》衰係邊度？","createTime":"2017-04-07T17:23:01.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-10T09:21:57.000Z","uid":85552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"7c7d31bbeffe61d48b02d735a5107682cb634d47","tid":191271,"uid":85552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T17:23:01.000Z","msg":"《分&middot;裂》衰係邊度？<br />\n<br />\n我覺得成套戲無論故事，演員，拍攝，所有野都好撚正<br />\n<br />\n但係就係衰係最後3分鐘<br />\n<br />\non9導演點都要拉返落佢之前部戲度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n好地地一部心理精神病電影，無啦啦變左超人片<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如果最後係beast頂完兩槍走左，講女主角俾人救左之後，轉鏡頭慢慢拉過去見到beast因為轉返其他性格頂唔順死左，然後女警察同本身性格內向既女主角講呀叔黎左接佢，佢由口口"},{"pid":"2b4dd5eb5063df9e2a0f8bf0fecd6464dc4d22c8","tid":191271,"uid":85552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T17:27:46.000Z","msg":"如果最後係beast頂完兩槍走左，講女主角俾人救左之後，轉鏡頭慢慢拉過去見到beast因為轉返其他性格頂唔順死左，然後女警察同本身性格內向既女主角講呀叔黎左接佢，佢由唔出聲望住個警察突然變左勁開朗咁回應個警察，表示佢經歷完呢件事之後都同男主角一樣開始有多重人格。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n咁個結局就正啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b3efa76d1f7abdfd2abb5d3361d7e36e410c916","tid":191271,"uid":29715,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T17:28:58.000Z","msg":"女主角無除剩個bra"},{"pid":"0f7c38c8498b843645f10724e5396cea3115c7cb","tid":191271,"uid":12820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T17:30:24.000Z","msg":"思裂呀嗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f4d2fda091d6c2e349a9fbde1196fa5c85b9f05","tid":191271,"uid":85552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T17:31:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>女主角無除剩個bra</blockquote><br />\n你岩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n由中段叫人除衫開始期待，點知等到最後都除唔晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead